## Limitations

The report is based on data available up to October 2023, and some sources may have more recent updates that are not included. Additionally, the projections and statistics are subject to change based on economic conditions, technological advancements, and consumer behavior shifts. The analysis primarily focuses on the United States and global trends, which may not fully represent regional variations in e-commerce growth.

